      <title>Trump administration ends 988 Lifeline's special service for LGBTQ+ young people</title>
      <author>Rhitu Chatterjee</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2025/07/19/nx-s1-5472593/988-suicide-crisis-lifeline-lgbtq</link>
